\frac{\displaystyle {n \choose N} {n-1 \choose N} {n-2 \choose N} ... {n-r+1 \choose N}}{\displaystyle {n \choose N}^{r}}
\displaystyle \frac{(n)_{Nr}}{(n_{N})^{r}}
